	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When background/sprite clipping is enabled in $2001 which palette color entry should be used for those left 8 screen pixels?  I can't seem to find an answer in existing documentation.  I'm hoping this isn't a totally dumb question...it's been an incredibly long time since I've messed with my PPU logic and I don't remember a lot of the intricacies. :-/
<br />
<br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
